---
description: Prevent TODO stubs and fake logic in deliverable code
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

# No Placeholder Logic

- Do not leave `501 Not implemented`, fake handlers, or temporary mock branches in merged code.
- Replace TODO stubs with real behavior, or gate unfinished features behind explicit feature flags.
- Remove debug-only network calls and console noise before completing a task.
- If a dependency is blocked, document a concrete follow-up task and safe fallback behavior.
- Treat "coming soon" UI copy as incomplete unless the route is intentionally disabled.
- Never present placeholder outputs as production-ready implementation.
